elements.name: Search for a product and verify its availability in offers page

steps.name: User should be able to navigate to the Greenkart website
User should be able to view the homepage
User searches for a product on the homepage with the shortname Ora
Extract the text of the filtered product on the homepage
User should be able to navigate to the Offers page
A new tab opens
User should search for the same product on the Offers page with the shortname Ora
Extract the text of the filtered product from the offers page
Verify that the product available on the homepage also exists on the Offers page
